title: which one should i prefer in kcet choice filling order

comments.body: Are you able to find PES RR campus in the college list. I couldn't find it. I searched the whole list multiple times
The college code for pes CSE is not CS, it's BW. The code for pes(rr) is E009
Last year cutoff was CS core was 15xx tho , so you should be getting that itself. Since RV increased it's seats this year,  PES cutoffs are bound to fall as well
Go to the course list and search for btech courses as pes offers only btech courses, then try searching that branch code
